Metrics.Name: http.server.request.duration
Metrics.Description: Measures the duration of inbound RPC.

Metrics.Name: http.server.request.body.size
Metrics.Description: Measures size of RPC request messages (uncompressed).

Metrics.Name: http.server.response.body.size
Metrics.Description: Measures size of RPC response messages (uncompressed).

Metrics.Name: http.server.active_requests
Metrics.Description: Measures the number of messages received per RPC. Should be 1 for all non-streaming RPCs.
